name: String
description: String

name: Yay! Kids! Trophy
description: Make the hotel fun for kids, too!

name: Top Notch Trophy
description: Spruce up your Pet Hotel! With staff and decorations, it will be world class in no time!

name: Bigger 'n Better Trophy
description: Keep on growing your awesome hotel!

name: Caring Bear Trophy (Step 1/4)
description: Happy, healthy, and loved pets make the best guests! Let's start by showing your pets some love and companionship. There's a special prize waiting for YOU at the end, so check your progress in the Guestbook!

name: Caring Bear Trophy (Step 2/4)
description: Next, visit Party Rooms so your pets can have a rip-roaring good time! Don't forget to see your progress in the Guest Book after your visit! You're one step closer to a special prize!

name: Caring Bear Trophy (Step 3/4)
description: Almost there! Can you hear those grumbling stomachs?! Better cook up a meal and feed your hungry pets! They'll be satisfied and you'll be on your way to a special prize!

name: Caring Bear Trophy (Step 4/4)
description: Your pets have that warm, fuzzy feeling from being well taken care of! You're the best! Go to the Guestbook and "Complete" your pet to get your prize!

name: Friendly Neighbor Trophy
description: Help out your neighbors! Visit neighbors and tap their coins and their pets will leave them a bigger tip! They'll be more likely to help you in return!

name: Ranking it in Trophy
description: As you improve your Social Rank, your neighbors are more likely to tap your coins! Tapping neighbors' coins will help you move up through the ranks!

name: Social Butterfly Trophy
description: Tap your neighbors' coins as often as possible and someday you might become a Hotel Billionaire!

name: Team Building Trophy
description: Staff will take care of all your pets' needs. Hire wisely, and your pets will thank you!

name: Connect the Dots Trophy
description: Pets love to travel around the hotel. Build connectors and they'll be free to roam!

name: Big 'ol Hotel Trophy
description: Build the biggest hotel in town!

name: 3 Star Super Star Trophy
description: Get a 3-star Rating for your Pet Hotel!

name: 4 Star Super Star Trophy
description: Get a 4-star Rating for your Pet Hotel!

name: 5 Star Super Star Trophy
description: Get a 5-star Rating for your Pet Hotel!

name: Bamboo Muncher Trophy
description: Which pet loves to munch bamboo? Build a Bamboo room to find out!

name: Jumpin' Jungle Trophy
description: Find out which mischievous pet lives in the jungle

name: Honey Slurpin'Trophy
description: Betty loves sweet honey! Build her a room so she can slurp honey all day!

name: Dark Cave Trophy
description: Flying mammals love dark caves! See who lives in this one!

name: Flamin' Dojo Trophy
description: The Dojo houses a mythical fiery pet, find out who he is and get some kids for him to wow!

name: Desert Dreamin' Trophy
description: Carrie the Camel loves the sand and the desert! Build her some sandy stuff!

name: Private Pirate Trophy
description: Ahoy, Matey! Time to construct a pirate's lair. First build a room for your little pirate, add 2 kids, then a wooden connector. Yarrr!

name: Running Pony Trophy
description: Polly the Pony loves to run indoors and outdoors! Build her a Workout room so she can be happy!

name: Treehouse Trophy
description: A cozy house in the treetops is the perfect place to take a snooze. Collect some twigs, then turn them into a treehouse!

name: Wet 'n Wild Trophy
description: Water, water everywhere! Build a water tank and some glass tubes. Then let the water flow in a wondrous waterfall!

name: Wise Ol' Trophy
description: Whoooo lives here? Here's a hint: he comes out after sunset, and he's very wise. That's whoooo!

name: Ring of Fire Trophy
description: After a volcano erupts, there's lots to clean up! Build a Volcano room, then pick up the fallen trees!

name: Furry Friends Trophy
description: Place some metal beams for your furry friends to climb on!

name: Asian Garden Trophy
description: In a busy city like Seoul, a roof garden provides the perfect place to relax.

name: Stargazer Trophy
description: Windswept cliff peaks are the perfect place to gaze up the stars. Build a Windswept fun room and Cliff Peak, then place your telescope on top!

name: Digging for Fossils Trophy
description: Let's go fossil hunting! Build a sandy path, then build a Fossil room!

name: Spring Flowers Trophy
description: Spring has sprung in your hotel! Build a Flower room and decorate with a flowering plant!

name: Hills 'n Clouds Trophy
description: Vacation time! Let's escape to the green hills and build a fun room in the clouds!

name: Mysteries of Atlantis Trophy
description: Deep beneath the waves lies the mysterious lost city of Atlantis. Explore Atlantis and the ocean reefs that surround it.

name: Starter Burster Trophy
description: Let the popping begin!

name: Beginner Burster Trophy
description: Pop a little more!

name: Medium Burster Trophy
description: Keep up the good poppin'!

name: Advanced Burster Trophy
description: Pop, pop, pop! Impressive popping!

name: Master Burster Trophy
description: Can't  stop popping!

name: Bronze Burster Trophy
description: My, my, what a good popper you are!

name: Silver Burster Trophy
description: Keep popping, and the Silver Burster Trophy will go to you!

name: Gold Burster Trophy
description: That's the sound of some truly great popping!

name: Platinum  Burster Trophy
description: You're tops! Congratulations on becoming the ultimate popping master!

name: Trillium Burster Trophy
description: You're tops! Congratulations on becoming the ultimate popping master!

name: Itsy Bitsy Happiness Trophy
description: The trophy may be itsy bitsy, but your pets will love you!

name: Mini Happiness Trophy
description: Mini trophy for a mini amount of love!

name: Tiny Happiness Trophy
description: Keep spreading the love!

name: Little Happiness Trophy
description: Spreading a little happiness wherever you go!

name: Pretty Big Happiness Trophy
description: Spreading the love in a pretty big way!

name: Big Big Happiness Trophy
description: The love keeps getting bigger and bigger!

name: Ginormous Happiness Trophy
description: Love, love everywhere! Your pets truly love you!

name: HUMONGOUS Happiness Trophy
description: You have so, so, so, so much love to give!

name: Doggy Day Care Trophy
description: Dogs will have fun hanging out together in your hotel! Build some rooms for dogs, then watch them play together!

name: Water Pets Trophy
description: Splish, Splash! Buy 3 rooms that aquatic pets could live in!

name: Pre-historic Trophy
description: Get all the Jurassic animals!

name: Mr. Buggy Trophy
description: Bugs like to creepy crawl, get 3 six-legged friends to play in your hotel!

name: Fitness First (Step 1/5)
description: The Hotel is looking great but you need to make sure our pets are staying fit and energetic! Let's build a Workout room so our pets have somewhere to stay in shape.

name: Fitness First (Step 2/5)
description: Wow! Just look at how much your pets love the Workout room! But after all that hard work they want somewhere to cool off. It's time to build them a Shower so they can relax after a hard workout.

name: Fitness First (Step 3/5)
description: Your Workout room and Shower combo are a huge success! You should find even more pets to come enjoy them. But first things first, you're going to need more space.

name: Fitness First (Step 4/5)
description: Great! Now you should get some really active pets to come check them out! I bet a kitty and a squirrel would have a great time here!

name: Fitness First (Step 5/5)
description: All of this exercise has really worked up your pets' appetites. They need a steady supply of food or they won't be able to keep exercising!

name: Birds of a Feather (Step 1/5)
description: There's a world-renowned bird watcher in town! I bet she'd love your hotel, but you need to find her first. Maybe she's somewhere in the neighborhood.

name: Birds of a Feather (Step 2/5)
description: There's no sign of her anywhere! Maybe you can bring HER to YOU. Make the hotel look as bird friendly as possible.

name: Birds of a Feather (Step 3/5)
description: Not a bad start, but still no sign of her. Maybe some baby birds and a space for them to play will catch her eye.

name: Birds of a Feather (Step 4/5)
description: She's still not here! You're going to need a really special bird to get her attention. You should try something big!

name: Birds of a Feather (Step 5/5)
description: She's here! She seems really interested in seeing an albatross family. Now all you have to do is raise one!

name: Think of the Kids (Step 1/5)
description: Your pets look like they want to have some fun! Why don't you hire a staff member who can entertain them?

name: Think of the Kids (Step 2/5)
description: ÌÂEver since I was little I've only ever wanted two things: a turtle and a bunny! Can you help my dream come true?Ì¨

name: Think of the Kids (Step 3/5)
description: ÌÂThe turtle and bunny are so cute! But do you know what's even cuter? Turtle and bunny babies!Ì¨

name: Think of the Kids (Step 4/5)
description: Look at how happy Ball Girl Ikumi and the new pets are! Let's keep up the cheer by getting even more baby pets!

name: Think of the Kids (Step 5/5)
description: These new pets are really livening up the place! But they're also creating a huge mess. Make sure your hotel stays ‰ÛÊclean as your pet families grow!

name: Beach bums! (Step 1/3)
description: Phew, it's hot out! On summer days like these, your pets need a beach day! Help them out!

name: Beach bums! (Step 2/3)
description: Surf's up! The pets love the the sand, but you need some  activities to make it a real beach party!

name: Beach bums! (Step 3/3)
description: Woohoo! Your pets had a blast rolling in the sand and worked up quite an appetite! Clean and feed them to complete your day at the beach!

name: Globe Trotter Trophy (Step 1/4)
description: Become a global hot spot! Don't forget to bring your passport! First stop: China!

name: Globe Trotter Trophy (Step 2/4)
description: What a whirlwind! Your hotel is becoming an exotic destination! Next stop: The land of smiles

name: Globe Trotter Trophy (Step 3/4)
description: You're a seasoned traveller! But are you ready to head farther north?! See you in Korea!

name: Globe Trotter Trophy (Step 4/4)
description: Your trip is almost complete! Better brush up on your Hindi. You're off to India!

name: Keep your cool! (Step 1/4)
description: The earth is getting warmer- have you done your part? Cool down your hotel to help the polar bears!

name: Keep your cool! (Step 2/4)
description: Great job! Mama bear is here, but she needs her cubs!

name: Keep your cool! (Step 3/4)
description: The whole polar family is here! Better prepare your hotel for the winter hibernation!

name: Keep your cool! (Step 4/4)
description: Brrrr! The cubs and mama bear feel right at home, but the staff are chilly! Help them warm up to make the whole hotel happy!
